{"type": "article", "id": 30350, "title": "平衡烛台", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-31T22:56:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160731200334ZJO4C1BKgrcGjYWF.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>你有没有见过会不断变化的烛台？一侧是燃烧的蜡烛，另一侧是圆柱形的黑色玄武岩，这个像天平一样的设计是阿姆斯特丹设计双人组合 <a href=\"http://www.bindesign.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Laura Bin</a> 的作品，<a href=\"http://www.lauraklinkenberg.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Laura Klinkenberg</a> 和 Bin Xu 两位设计师希望通过它展现出土与火两大元素之间动态关系。随着蜡烛因燃烧而不断减重，纤细的黄铜组件会随之不断调整位置维持平衡。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/the-rising-balance-candleholder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 85 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731200350SZzONiusPCj5FYXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731200350DhNQG2cqUVHrS31v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731200350U4HcOjytSDkliCeg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731200351LE2WOPVMJfABDwq1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}